with version stable 1.1.3 1.1.2
with also    --disable-static
with role    utility
with trait   console library makej multilib-dual optimize
with source  http://bitmath.org/code/mtdev/mtdev-$VERSION.tar.bz2
with info    last 20120822
with info    home http://bitmath.org/code/mtdev/
with info    cite 'library converts kernel MT events to slotted type B protocol
The mtdev is a stand-alone library which transforms
all variants of kernel MT events to the slotted type B protocol.
The events put into mtdev may be from any MT device,
specifically type A without contact tracking,
type A with documentation for further details.'
